@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333
@appCode = MYTASCO
@token = demo-U001

### COP-compatible staff search
POST {{baseUrl}}/mytasco/v1/staff/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-App-Code: {{appCode}}
X-Locale: vi-VN
X-Timezone: Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "example": { "keyword": "Nguyễn", "status": 1 },
  "pageInfo": { "pageSize": 5, "currentPage": 0 }
}

### COP-compatible organization graph
GET {{baseUrl}}/mytasco/v1/organization/tree?depth=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-App-Code: {{appCode}}

### Permission-aware knowledge search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/search?userId=U001&q=khung%20lương&language=vi

### Grounded automotive-distribution accounting answer (Employee)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "AUTO-FIN-EMP",
  "question": "What is the dealer network month-end close sequence?",
  "language": "en"
}

### Same network question (Employee accounting view)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "AUTO-FIN-EMP",
  "question": "How is the automotive distribution network performing this month?",
  "language": "en"
}

### Same network question (Executive view)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "AUTO-FIN-EXEC",
  "question": "How is the automotive distribution network performing this month?",
  "language": "en"
}

### Provably invisible Restricted M&A source
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "AUTO-FIN-EMP",
  "question": "Which dealer acquisition or M&A targets are under review?",
  "language": "en"
}

### Sticky history for the Accounting Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/ask?userId=AUTO-FIN-EMP

### Rendered example Q&A deliverable
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspace/examples
